18:- What are the media types allowed by css?
Ans:- media allowed by css types
    
        All   :-  Used for all media type devices (default)

        print  :- Used for printers

        screen :- Used for smartphones,computer screen , tablets, etc..

        speech :- Used for screen readers.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

19:- What is rule set?
Ans:- css ruleset is various affirmations to various pieces or element of the document.the objective is to apply a bunch of properties for certain distinct qualities to a solitary or a particular components in the connected html page

example of 


    h1{
        color:blue;
    }

    h1 -> is a selector

    color -> is a property

    Blue -> is Value


    

